各方面采取严厉措施以「修复国家的根基」。（央视新闻）消息人士称英国实际财政亏空不止 220 亿英镑"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-f018843a29900275e5ae4d155c522ad6_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/666166316"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI67mouJb2y9RZEAMaCTExMDMxNDkxMSDRk9+2BjAAOOMBQARyCTY2NjE2NjMxNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1725704508.475301", "card_id": "Q_275825797", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "目前哪个汽车厂商的新能源技术能力储备比较强？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "还有对于厂商而言，有自主研发电池管理系统和电机的必要吗？谢谢！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-fbb63cb42b01b0d6ee96e6e982bb3d18_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/275825797"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I67mouJb2y9RZEAMaCDIzNTcwMjc1INakr9cFMAA4sQJABXIJMjc1ODI1Nzk3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1725704508.475507", "card_id": "Q_666357223", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 94}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "苹果 AppStore 已发布微信 iOS 8.0.51 版本，这一消息背后透露出哪些信息？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "苹果应用商店显示，北京时间 9 月 6 日下午，苹果 AppStore 现已更新微信 iOS 8.0.51 版本。苹果 AppStore 已发布微信 iOS 8.0.51 版本 _ 显示"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a0e3dfdc1084c4e5a456c536fd64448f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "39 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "tr